```{r pancreas 32034575, include=FALSE}

PMID_32034575 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32034575', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32034575 <- paste0(PMID_32034575$journal,' ', PMID_32034575$year, ' ', PMID_32034575$month,';', PMID_32034575$volume,'(', PMID_32034575$number,'):', PMID_32034575$pages)

PubMed_32034575 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32034575$eprint)

doi_32034575 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32034575$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
